                    <span>A great explanation of how the current state of programming came to be. However, the depth of this book is very simplistic, and won't hold the interest of anyone whose done more than a level 100 programming course.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">What does it mean to be a programmer, in a Nutshell</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
